name: Meal-a-Day Calendars!
description: Tired of the same old meals every day? This will help get you out of the "What's for dinner?" slump! A year's worth of meal ideas that you can use for lunch OR dinner, INCLUDING a shopping list for each month. No more staring in the fridge to see what you can put together, or worrying about whether or not you used up the last can of tuna, because each shopping list includes everything you'll need for that month's meals! A terrific tool for any busy Parent, Couple, or Caregiver! Give it a try, and after you do, you'll never want to shop without it!
